---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: 'Is this a timeshare?',
    a: 'No. This is equity co-ownership of real property, not a timeshare. Investors hold actual ownership stakes in the asset, not a bundle of usage rights. The exact legal structure will be documented clearly before any commitment is required.'
  },
  {
    q: 'How does priority reservation work?',
    a: 'Investors receive priority access to reserve stays for up to 4 months per year, typically during the peak village season from December through April. The priority booking window opens first for investors. Any remaining availability then opens to the broader community after the investor window closes. Exact rules will be defined in the investor agreement.'
  },
  {
    q: 'Can I stay at the property outside the priority window?',
    a: 'Yes. Outside the investor priority window, stays can be booked through the regular hospitality channel, subject to availability. Your investor status does not limit your total time at the property. It guarantees your first access to the best windows.'
  },
  {
    q: 'What happens to operating revenue during years 1 through 5?',
    a: 'During the first five years, operating income from the property is targeted to be reinvested into upgrades, infrastructure, land stewardship, and the guest experience. This is the designed intention to increase long-term value before any income distributions to investors. Subject to final legal documentation and actual results. This is not a promise of any specific outcome.'
  },
  {
    q: 'What are the risks?',
    a: 'Real estate involves meaningful risk. Property values can decrease. Operating businesses can underperform projections. Legal and regulatory environments in Brazil can change. Currency fluctuations affect the value of your investment in your home currency. This is not a guaranteed investment. We encourage every prospective investor to conduct thorough independent due diligence with qualified legal and financial advisors before making any decision.'
  },
  {
    q: 'What is the legal structure?',
    a: 'The legal structure is being finalized. We will share full documentation before any commitment is required. Do not make any investment decision before reviewing the investor agreement with your own qualified legal counsel. We will not rush this process.'
  },
  {
    q: 'How do I exit or transfer my stake?',
    a: 'Exit and transfer mechanics will be defined in the investor agreement. We plan to include provisions for investor transfers, subject to agreed conditions and approval processes. This will be a defined process, not an open market. Details to be confirmed.'
  },
  {
    q: 'What is the next step?',
    a: 'Request the investor deck. It includes property documentation, the investment structure overview, programming plans, and a due diligence checklist. After reviewing, we schedule a call to answer your questions. There is no pressure and no obligation at any stage. Capacity in the investor circle is limited to maintain community quality.'
  }
];
---

<section class="faq" id="faq">
  <div class="container container-narrow">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center">Common Questions</h2>
    <p class="lead text-center text-muted">
      Straightforward answers to the things investors typically ask.
    </p>

    <div class="faq-list">
      {faqs.map((item) => (
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="faq-question">{item.q}</h3>
          <p class="faq-answer">{item.a}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="faq-disclaimer">
      <p>
        <strong>Legal notice:</strong> Nothing on this website constitutes a solicitation
        to invest, a guarantee of any return, or legal or financial advice. All investment
        details, legal structure, and terms are subject to final documentation. This is
        not a public offering. Prospective investors should consult qualified legal and
        financial advisors independently before making any decision.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .faq-list {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .faq-item {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .faq-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .faq-question {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .faq-disclaimer {
    background: #fff8e6;
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-left: 3px solid #d4a012;
  }

  .faq-disclaimer p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .faq-disclaimer strong {
    color: #8b6914;
  }
</style>
